I have created the Text feature developer guide at `generated/text.md`. The document covers:

- **Text Style Effects**: Underline, Shadow, Outline, LineThrough, and Bevel with configuration examples
- **Font Styling**: FontWeight, FontWidth, and FontSlant enumerations
- **Input Filtering**: InputFilter with allow/deny patterns and rejection handling
- **Font Variations**: FontVariationAxis for variable fonts
- **Dynamic Font Sizing**: FitRange and FitCandidate for automatic font fitting

All code examples are adapted from the sample files in `repos/dali-ui/samples/text/` and use the dali-ui View-based object model (Label, InputField) as required.
